quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  23,18,"Men jippini immorde ka kammu ndiyam e emmbere [haaju tagu ngun], Men ndewni …óam ka leydi, pellet, Menen ko Men Hattan…ìe e dow na…ìugol …óam"
  23,19,"Men fu…ó…óani on sabu majjam gese immorde e tamarooje e inabuuje, no woodani on nder ton dim…óe …óuu…óu…óe ko e majje √±aamoton"
  23,20,"E leggal ngal no yalta immorde to Tuuri Siinaa hingal fu…óina gu∆¥am [nebban wujetee…óam] e li'am [maafir…óam] wonannde √±aamoo…ìe"
  23,21,"Pellet, no woodani on e neemoraa…ói …óin tasakuyee, Me…óen yarna on go…ó…óun e ko woni kon ka deedi majji, no woodani on e majji nafaaji …óuu…óu…ói, ko immorde e majji kadi √±aamoton"
  23,22,Ko e hoore-majji e hoore laa…óe …óen ronndete…óon
  23,23,"Gom…óii Men Nulii Nuuhu e yim…ìe makko …ìen, o maaki : \"Ko onon yo yim…ìe am, rewee Alla. Rewetee…óo alanaa on ko woori Mo. Enee, on hulatah"
  23,24,"Hooree…ìe mbatu ngun wi'ani …ìen yeddu…ìe immorde e yim…ìe makko …ìen: \"Oo wonaali si ko o …ìanndinke yeru mo'on himo faalaa nde o …ìurnotoo e dow moo…óon. Sinndo Alla muuyino O jippinayno Malaa'ikaa…ìe, men naniraali …óum baabiraa…ìe amen aran…ìe …ìen"
  23,25,"Kanko o wonaali si wanaa ko o gorko mo jinna woni e mu'un, habbitee mo tun haa see…óa"
  23,26,"O maaki: \"Joom am, wallam e ko …ìe fennimi kon"
  23,27,"Men wahayini faade e makko yo o lesu laana kan e dennka Amen e Wahayu Amen, si Yamiroore Amen nden arii hu…ì…ìinirde nden pullitike [ndiyam] naadu e nder makka immorde e kala nooneeji …óin …ói…ói-…ói…ói. E koreeji ma, si wanaa …ìen konngol ngol aditii e mu'un, wata a haaldu e am fii …ìen too√±u…ìe, pellet, kam…ìe ko …ìe yooletee…ìe"
